	<div class="contentwide">
		<h2>Summary:</h2><div class="infobox">Upon acquiring the Alien Ecology technology, your Worker units and the Miasmic Condenser orbital unit can place miasma in tiles. To place miasma with a Worker unit, it will have the option among its Actions to be ordered to “Add Miasma.” The number of turns to add the miasma is indicated when you hover the cursor over the order. Upon completion, the miasma is immediately placed on the map.<br /><br />The Miasmic Condenser, once placed, will add miasma to hexes, starting in its placement hex and radiating outward.</div>
